[{"id":"9cebbfa68fb29d4270b31c70eb8e8998","from":"Unknown","from_email":"updates@research.f1000.com","to":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","to_list":[{"name":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"Publish your labs' antibody validation studies for free!","date":"2015-06-24T14:05:03.000Z","formatted_date":"Jun 24, 2015","formatted_time":"2:05 PM","body":"To ensure you receive F1000Research emails, add updates@research.f1000.com: http://p5tre.emv3.com/HS?b=A71fPKGbMjFZm8b4WTCmZXfGW85MC1Hrfw0gSYJCrpYyTptco-p2Gq86z75L_ZQ4&c=qub5krbdqWtBYHT70nlZpg\n to your safe list. View web version. : http://p5tre.emv3.com/HM?b=CdDtvTLVnPGAlcmpoW3vaAygHt8s_zwvqGYkjxA6iK7fHPOphiKU_CWEU0KXf45m&c=kYFlK40euAxEruyKKqalQw\n\n\n: http://p5tre.emv3.com/HS?b=T2G8W-uXMO6vro0KX-PZnQ2Tpq6srgDN7Gs_MFq_o9Yxwz0IAj0MlOgCo0HGL5gs&c=_EMZMgA-ukuik6haIF8K3g\nDear Jeff, \n\nWould you like to contribute to a growing resource which will enhance \nthe reliability and reproducibility of antibodies in scientific \nresearch? \n\n\nF1000Research, together with an experienced group of advisors, recently launched an Antibody Validation article collection: http://p5tre.emv3.com/HS?b=xtRZqIFnnhRikBYX1dA2LvD3SElPnU_6Xn9l5Go_NNX2u4OEDLrYPnLOauXc9eW4&c=D-HwTqJbgbMS3saM05PCwA\n to provide a platform for researchers and companies to validate \nantibodies, share their results with the scientific community and \nreceive credit for the important experimental work they have done. \n\n\nWith thanks to financial support from our sponsors*, all studies in the \nAntibody Validation Channel will be published FREE of charge throughout \n2015. \n\nFREE SUBMISSION! \n\nQuote \"MUAV1\" in the Promotional Code box of our submission form to \nredeem your waiver. \n\n\n: http://p5tre.emv3.com/HS?b=lDoLbko0Dl_5yd-2D-PdyY3fh86MmAFK0Qozx2j_dXtTqaJXGESDFoBQDr-zWPEc&c=_UTUA0F5OMY4q9WT1LDyNQ\nExpires December 31, 2015 \nTo find out more, contact us at research@f1000.com: http://p5tre.emv3.com/HS?b=BbAjwXgTBNDzLSrKMJWoQvNgTeRsyDXyTwlpig0QwdNjJyGl5hn0gAsAN1NwDHjD&c=RUEhYDmDcp9xPhohxH07EA\n.\n\nThe F1000Research Team \n\n*F1000Research would like to thank Novus Biologicals, R&D Systems and Bio-Rad \nLaboratories for their sponsorship of the Antibody Validation Article \nChannel, thus enabling F1000Research to waive article processing charges for researchers who wish to \npublish their antibody validation studies on the platform. \n\n: http://p5tre.emv3.com/HS?b=a56z13zZBCMDZZqnFKS5WyiMWTSyzC5Di95G90UiG96qAhPSl_52Jrb0k8SVPT0M&c=IDTy8CpTNK_csuqgAIK4wQ\n\n: http://p5tre.emv3.com/HS?b=0h4oyQNCYLc9OZZ49xJLhC6KoEiZKhXDu-N-TfZ9JkDuU5NfuinNbYj37cUZcH1L&c=4hCygFRdsAezBQr0vz9qVQ\n\n: http://p5tre.emv3.com/HS?b=Knvex3x48m6CcNCLr-aTHioQUoZUeI1C3wDWbrDzLW6gnk3xUlHcllkStIIi07-_&c=Meeg8oAXIph_WZ5sCJN7oA\n\n: http://p5tre.emv3.com/HS?b=t4PvOfl4LCJOD5c4HxuBdx8osQvoheZV4--2X-a6dNUwWdAyGebeYHhNhJ1ruP-P&c=SCWMZu2aukkvC198h5EiHg\nF1000Research is an Open Science publishing platform for life scientists offering:\n\n\n * Immediate publication \n\n * Transparent refereeing \n\n * No editorial bias \n\n * Inclusion of all source data\nYou have received this message in the belief that it would be of \ninterest. To stop receiving this type of information from F1000Research, click here to unsubscribe: http://p5tre.emv3.com/HD?b=xRX6fHMeNccQWKVO1M16xIkIQbQeMGtPAU7BEyH0aqdjlrx0dNvwSr8MiW0CD_s4&c=iGsBKOlKJIMoj7pMnKEt-w\n. For further information or enquiries please contact publishers@f1000.com: http://p5tre.emv3.com/HS?b=uXiKwWJzciqMz14qsn401z8QVGJQdSfXHGpTqlJMWQdfEYm21OMG6Cl3h6udBPgy&c=FynfGtmF4Zm-6chCGzphJA\n.\n\nF1000 Research Ltd | Science Navigation Group \nRegistered in England and Wales with Company Number 08322928. \nMiddlesex House | 34-42 Cleveland Street | London W1T 4LB | United \nKingdom \n\n","body_html":"<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/loose.dtd\"><html style=\"margin: 0;padding: 0;\"><head><meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" conten