llspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"table-layout: fixed; border: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; border: 0px solid transparent;\"><tr><td class=\"sf-td\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; border: 0px solid transparent; width: 100%;\"\n><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"table-layout: fixed; border: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><tr><td class=\"sf-html sf-td\" style=\"padding: 13px; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\"\n><p style=\"color: #77808b;font-family: Arial;font-size: 12px;mso-line-height-rule: exactly;line-height: 114%;font-weight: normal;font-style: normal;text-transform: none;margin-top: 0.5em;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0.5em;padding: 0;\">Dear Jeff, <br></p\n><p style=\"color: #77808b;font-family: Arial;font-size: 12px;mso-line-height-rule: exactly;line-height: 114%;font-weight: normal;font-style: normal;text-transform: none;margin-top: 0.5em;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0.5em;padding: 0;\"></p></td></tr></table></td></tr></table\n><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"table-layout: fixed; border: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; border: 0px solid transparent;\"><tr><td class=\"sf-td\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; border: 0px solid transparent; width: 50%;\"\n><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"table-layout: fixed; border: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><tr><td class=\"sf-html sf-td\" style=\"padding: 13px; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\"\n><p style=\"color: #77808b;font-family: Arial;font-size: 12px;mso-line-height-rule: exactly;line-height: 114%;font-weight: normal;font-style: normal;text-transform: none;margin-top: 0.5em;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0.5em;padding: 0;\"><b>Would you like to contribute to a growing resource which will enhance the reliability and reproducibility of antibodies in scientific research?</b> <br><br></p\n><p style=\"color: #77808b;font-family: Arial;font-size: 12px;mso-line-height-rule: exactly;line-height: 114%;font-weight: normal;font-style: normal;text-transform: none;margin-top: 0.5em;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0.5em;padding: 0;\"><i>F1000Research</i\n>, together with an experienced group of advisors, recently launched an <a target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: #f2673c;font-family: Arial;font-size: 12px;font-weight: normal;font-style: normal;text-transform: none;text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"http://p5tre.emv3.com/HS?b=xtRZqIFnnhRikBYX1dA2LvD3SElPnU_6Xn9l5Go_NNX2u4OEDLrYPnLOauXc9eW4&c=D-HwTqJbgbMS3saM05PCwA\">Antibody Validation article collection</a> to provide a platform for researchers and companies to validate antibodies, share their results with the scientific community and receive credit for the important experimental work they have done. <br\n><br></p><p style=\"color: #77808b;font-family: Arial;font-size: 12px;mso-line-height-rule: exactly;line-height: 114%;font-weight: normal;font-style: normal;text-transform: none;margin-top: 0.5em;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0.5em;padding: 0;\">With thanks to financial support from our sponsors*, all studies in the Antibody Validation Channel will be published FREE of charge throughout 2015. <br></p\n><p style=\"color: #77808b;font-family: Arial;font-size: 12px;mso-line-height-rule: exactly;line-height: 114%;font-weight: normal;font-style: normal;text-transform: none;margin-top: 0.5em;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0.5em;padding: 0;\"></p></td></tr></table></td\n><td class=\"sf-td\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; border: 1px solid #acb3bb; background-color: #f0f0f0; width: 50%;\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"table-layout: fixed; border: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><tr\n><td class=\"sf-td\" style=\"height:10px;border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><div style=\"height:10px;\"></div></td></tr></table><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" style=\"table-layout: fixed; border: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><tr\n><td class=\"sf-html sf-td\" style=\"padding: 13px; border-collapse: collapse; mso-table-lspace: 0pt; mso-table-rspace: 0pt; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><p style=\"color: #77808b;font-family: Arial;font-size: 12px;mso-line-height-rule: exactly;line-height: 114%;font-weight: normal;font-style: normal;text-transform: none;margin-top: 0.5em;margin-left: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0.5em;padding: 0;text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><b\n><font style=\"line-height: 26px; font-size: 26px;\" color=\"#f2673c\">FREE SUBMISSION! </font></b></p><p style=